e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4601fb41fb6dc02131f74d801fd266dfb184e72","tid":2142790,"uid":67840,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"ddce62ec78cebf2ce850881efd5cabbfa11a0de8","tid":2142790,"uid":125026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"#BoycottMulan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T20:10:15.000Z","msg":"人地撐木蘭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係想發洩disney 唔上套戲搞到佢間戲院無得賺錢<br />\n唔好炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe cinema owner explained that he decided to make the vid to express his frustration after hearing about Disney&rsquo;s decision. He said that he has been promoting Mulan &ldquo;for months&rdquo; and that he and his fellow operators had hoped the film would be a key title to boost their re-opening efforts.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It&rsquo;s really a huge effort to stay open right now for most of us, but we were assuming there would be some ambitious movie releases in the coming weeks,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;By losing Mulan, we lost the possibility of offering our audiences a long-awaited film that would have helped us after these past hard weeks. It is also a bad message to send to the public [who had been expecting a theatrical release].&rdquo;"},{"pid":"f539f8a9ae844fe3b4581b9776df2c62ae8a7253","tid":2142790,"uid":120205,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b4601fb41fb6dc02131f74d801fd266dfb184e72","tid":2142790,"uid":67840,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"ddce62ec78cebf2ce850881efd5cabbfa11a0de8","tid":2142790,"uid":125026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"#BoycottMulan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T20:10:15.000Z","msg":"人地撐木蘭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係想發洩disney 唔上套戲搞到佢間戲院無得賺錢<br />\n唔好炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe cinema owner explained that he decided to make the vid to express his frustration after hearing about Disney&rsquo;s decision. He said that he has been promoting Mulan &ldquo;for months&rdquo; and that he and his fellow operators had hoped the film would be a key title to boost their re-opening efforts.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It&rsquo;s really a huge effort to stay open right now for most of us, but we were assuming there would be some ambitious movie releases in the coming weeks,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;By losing Mulan, we lost the possibility of offering our audiences a long-awaited film that would have helped us after these past hard weeks. It is also a bad message to send to the public [who had been expecting a theatrical release].&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T20:23:38.000Z","msg":"炒撚哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://deadline.com/2020/08/french-cinema-owner-destroys-mulan-pop-up-art-protest-disneys-decision-skip-cinemas-1203005960/amp/?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2020%2F08%2Ffrench-cinema-owner-destroys-mulan-pop-up-art-protest-disneys-decision-skip-cinemas-1203005960%2Famp%2F%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=91f9519e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://deadline.com/2020/08/french-cinema-owner-destroys-mulan-pop-up-art-protest-disneys-decision-skip-cinemas-1203005960/amp/?__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"514be73e5fd5b05996a6ba48bce2ccae426b7db1","tid":2142790,"uid":120205,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a1684a00801048ee9110e78ec1f361dfa24b6da7","tid":2142790,"uid":331821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":